{"tha-ap330:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap330:0.2":"Umapupphiyavagga ","tha-ap330:0.3":"8 Sumanaveliyattheraapadana ","tha-ap330:1.1":"“Vessabhussa bhagavato, ","tha-ap330:1.2":"lokajetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap330:1.3":"Sabbe jana samagamma, ","tha-ap330:1.4":"mahapujam karonti te. ","tha-ap330:2.1":"Sudhaya pindam katvana, ","tha-ap330:2.2":"avelam sumanayaham; ","tha-ap330:2.3":"Sihasanassa purato, ","tha-ap330:2.4":"abhiropesaham tada. ","tha-ap330:3.1":"Sabbe jana samagamma, ","tha-ap330:3.2":"pekkhanti pupphamuttamam; ","tha-ap330:3.3":"Kenidam pujitam puppham, ","tha-ap330:3.4":"buddhasetthassa tadino. ","tha-ap330:4.1":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap330:4.2":"nimmanam upapajjaham; ","tha-ap330:4.3":"Anubhomi sakam kammam, ","tha-ap330:4.4":"pubbe sukatamattano. ","tha-ap330:5.1":"Yam yam yonupapajjami, ","tha-ap330:5.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","tha-ap330:5.3":"Sabbesanam piyo homi, ","tha-ap330:5.4":"pupphapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap330:6.1":"Nabhijanami kayena, ","tha-ap330:6.2":"vacaya uda cetasa; ","tha-ap330:6.3":"Samyatanam tapassinam, ","tha-ap330:6.4":"katam akkositam maya. ","tha-ap330:7.1":"Tena sucaritenaham, ","tha-ap330:7.2":"cittassa panidhihi ca; ","tha-ap330:7.3":"Sabbesam pujito homi, ","tha-ap330:7.4":"anakkosassidam phalam. ","tha-ap330:8.1":"Ito ekadase kappe, ","tha-ap330:8.2":"sahassarosi khattiyo; ","tha-ap330:8.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap330:8.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap330:9.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap330:9.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap330:9.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap330:10.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sumanaveliyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap330:11.1":"Sumanaveliyattherassapadanam atthamam. "}